sg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab50671c02a82f2afb13ed8cf6a754d32f963d7","tid":663673,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"支那人先中意食姐"},{"pid":"e105856358385ced13ba38de4bce5eba4b000308","tid":663673,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:02:21.000Z","msg":"唔好計有冇毒，本身就難食到狗也不屌<br />\n肉又少又臭，要靠d 重味將原本既味蓋過"},{"pid":"f94704dbaa1048eae00ca4f6a9dbef8926f5df30","tid":663673,"uid":90742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"唔係 一路有用黎做高湯？"},{"pid":"bf32ce2f6cc620dfbf84729b8528b7716622c8db","tid":663673,"uid":91685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"小龍蝦天敵係強國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}